response.original_title: Transworld Motocross Presents: Moto Skills with Nick Wey
response.overview: TransWorld Motocross presents MOTO Skills, with Nick Wey, the most complete and comprehensive how-to-ride movie ever made for motocross. With 17 years of professional racing experience, Wey has plenty of knowledge to share with viewers in an easy to understand, and entertaining manner. Thanks to the beauty of 240 fps slow motion, MOTO Skills breaks down riding techniques and utilizes visual callouts, as well as narration from Wey, to explain each technique in detail. Whether you’re a casual rider or hard core racer, MOTO Skills, with Nick Wey, is a film not to be missed!
response.tagline: TransWorld Motocross presents MOTO Skills, with Nick Wey, the most complete and comprehensive how-to-ride movie ever made for motocross. Whether you’re a casual rider or hard core racer, this film is not to be missed!
